What you need to know:

“The Engineer” swept the Player of the Year award in 2020 J1 League and Golden Boot two weeks ago after scoring 28 goals as Reysol marked their return to the top tier with a seventh-place finishIt also provides a good opportunity for Kashiwa to add another Levain Cup to their cabinet after winning the 1999 and 2013 titlesPrevious results between these two sides show that this will be a close contest